	<div id="popmake-454" class="pum-container popmake theme-414 pum-responsive pum-responsive-medium responsive size-medium main-container">

				
				
		
				<div class="pum-content popmake-content" tabindex="0">
			<div data-parent="true" class="vc_row style-color-xsdn-bg row-container" id="row-unique-0"><div class="row limit-width row-parent"><div class="wpb_row row-inner"><div class="wpb_column pos-top pos-center align_left column_parent col-lg-12 single-internal-gutter"><div class="uncol style-light"  ><div class="uncoltable"><div class="uncell no-block-padding" ><div class="uncont" ><div class="icon-box icon-box-top  icon-media-image" ><div class="icon-box-icon fa-container" style="width:60px;"><span class="text-accent-color btn-disable-hover"><img decoding="async" class=" srcset-async srcset-auto" src="https://www.andromeda-shipping.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/savety-1.png" width="200" height="200" alt=""  data-no-bp="" data-bp="720,1032" data-uniqueid="607-147883" data-guid="https://www.andromeda-shipping.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/savety-1.png" data-path="2024/10/savety-1.png" data-width="200" data-height="200" data-singlew="12" data-singleh="" data-crop="" loading="lazy" data-srcset="https://www.andromeda-shipping.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/savety-1.png 200w, https://www.andromeda-shipping.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/savety-1-150x150.png 150w" srcset="data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMjAwIiBoZWlnaHQ9IjIwMCIgeG1sbnM9Imh0dHA6Ly93d3cudzMub3JnLzIwMDAvc3ZnIj48cGF0aCBkPSJNMCAwaDF2MUgweiIgZmlsbD0ibm9uZSIgZmlsbC1ydWxlPSJldmVub2RkIi8+PC9zdmc+" /></span></div><div class="icon-box-content"><div class="icon-box-heading icon-box-fa-1x"><h3 class="h4 font-weight-600">SAFETY &amp; QUALITY</h3></div>
<p class="p1">IAS aims to provide healthy and safe working conditions, to promote safety and have pollution-free and environmentally safe operating practices.<br />
</p>
<p class="p1">In IAS, Safety takes precedence and is pursued and implemented, strictly and religiously.<br />
</p>
<p class="p1">The company has a proactive safety culture in place.<br />
</p>
<p class="p1">Initiatives to integrate and implement strict safety measures for protection and preservation of the environment have helped to uphold company’s non-compromising attitude towards safety.<br />
</p>
<p class="p1">In doing so, a key performance driver is the current edition of Tanker Management and Self-Assessment (TMSA) programme. We have built an Integrated Management System (IMS) for all our ships &amp; management offices.<br />
</p>
<p class="p1">TMSA and other industry guidelines such as Exxon Mobil MESQAC are the backbone upon which our operating procedures are based.<br />
</p>
<p class="p1">We work in compliance with the internationally recognized OHSAS 18001 and International Safety Management (ISM) standards. But standards alone are not enough. We strive to embed safety into personal actions.<br />
</p>
<p class="p1">Ships face threats from terrorism &amp; Piracy for which adequate counter measures have been provided. We take all necessary measures including industry-recognized, best practices on board our vessels to provide the highest level of security for our employees and customers.<br />
</p>
<p class="p1">Our environmental management system is certified to the international ISO 14001 standard and we invest significantly in lowering emissions and optimizing energy efficiency.<br />
</p>
<p class="p1">Our quality assurance process exceeds ISO 9001 standards. We continuously review and improve our ISM system with feedback from day-to-day operations, customers and stakeholders, operational performances and trends reporting.<br />
</p>
<p>&nbsp;<br /></p>
</div></div></div></div></div></div></div><script id="script-row-unique-0" data-row="script-row-unique-0" type="text/javascript" class="vc_controls">UNCODE.initRow(document.getElementById("row-unique-0"));</script></div></div></div>
		</div>

				
							<button type="button" class="pum-close popmake-close" aria-label="Close">
			Close			</button>
		
	</div>

</div>
