			<div data-parent="true" class="vc_row row-container" id="row-unique-5"><div class="row limit-width row-parent"><div class="wpb_row row-inner"><div class="wpb_column pos-top pos-center align_left column_parent col-lg-12 single-internal-gutter"><div class="uncol style-light"  ><div class="uncoltable"><div class="uncell no-block-padding" ><div class="uncont" ><div class="icon-box icon-box-top  icon-media-image" ><div class="icon-box-icon fa-container" style="width:60px;"><span class="text-accent-color btn-disable-hover"><img decoding="async" class=" srcset-async srcset-auto" src="https://www.andromeda-shipping.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/crew-manag-1.png" width="200" height="200" alt=""  data-no-bp="" data-bp="720,1032" data-uniqueid="612-198829" data-guid="https://www.andromeda-shipping.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/crew-manag-1.png" data-path="2024/10/crew-manag-1.png" data-width="200" data-height="200" data-singlew="12" data-singleh="" data-crop="" loading="lazy" data-srcset="https://www.andromeda-shipping.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/crew-manag-1.png 200w, https://www.andromeda-shipping.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/crew-manag-1-150x150.png 150w" srcset="data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMjAwIiBoZWlnaHQ9IjIwMCIgeG1sbnM9Imh0dHA6Ly93d3cudzMub3JnLzIwMDAvc3ZnIj48cGF0aCBkPSJNMCAwaDF2MUgweiIgZmlsbD0ibm9uZSIgZmlsbC1ydWxlPSJldmVub2RkIi8+PC9zdmc+" /></span></div><div class="icon-box-content"><div class="icon-box-heading icon-box-fa-1x"><h3 class="h4 font-weight-600">CREW MANAGEMENT</h3></div><p class="p1"><span class="s1">Crew Management service is our company’s core expertise. We undertake complete direct crew </span>recruitment<span class="s1">, management </span>and  Training activities <span class="s1">for our vessels and FSO</span> from our Andromeda office in Mumbai, India<br />
Developed training programs with Value added courses well exceeding the STCW requirements are carried out from our in-house training centre</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1">We provide equal opportunity in the career development of our seafarers. We believe that our crews are our partners in our growth and stability. </span></p>
<p class="p2">We consider training and professionalism of crew on board as crucial as any other requirements and we make sure that our efforts to maintain high quality standards are transmitted on board through our seafarers.</p>
<p class="p2">We are proud of our crew !</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
